#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:1
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:3
msgid ""
"The `VTKHDF` file format is a file format relying on [HDF5](https://www."
"hdfgroup.org/solutions/hdf5/). It is meant to provide good I/O performance "
"as well as robust and flexible parallel I/O capabilities."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:6
msgid ""
"It currently supports basic types: `PolyData`, `UnstructuredGrid`, "
"`ImageData`, `HyperTreeGrid` and composite types such as `OverlappingAMR`, "
"`MultiBlockDataSet` and the `PartitionedDataSetCollection`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:8
msgid "The current file format version is **2.5**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:11
msgid "Python examples and tutorial"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:13
msgid ""
"To help adopters use the VTKHDF File Format, we provide a repository : "
"[vtkhdf-script](https://gitlab.kitware.com/keu-public/vtkhdf/vtkhdf-scripts)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:15
msgid "It contains several folders:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:16
msgid ""
"[tutorial](https://gitlab.kitware.com/keu-public/vtkhdf/vtkhdf-scripts/-/"
"tree/main/tutorial): a complete tutorial showing how to create VTKHDF files "
"from scratch, incrementally adding more features."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:17
msgid ""
"[scripts](https://gitlab.kitware.com/keu-public/vtkhdf/vtkhdf-scripts/-/tree/"
"main/scripts): sample python scripts showing how to create VTKHDF files "
"using `h5py` for most of the data types currently supported by the format, "
"including temporal files."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:18
msgid ""
"[vtkxml-to-vtkhdf](https://gitlab.kitware.com/keu-public/vtkhdf/vtkhdf-"
"scripts/-/tree/main/vtkxml-to-vtkhdf) folder which contains script to "
"convert vtkxml file into vtk using the `vtkHDFWriter`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:21
msgid "Valuable documentation from blog posts"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:23
msgid ""
"[an overview of the first version and the motivation behind HDF5 in VTK]"
"(https://www.kitware.com/vtk-hdf-reader/)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:26
msgid "Extension"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:28
msgid ""
"The ` VTKHDF` format generally uses the `.vtkhdf` extension. The `.hdf` "
"extension is also supported but is not preferred. There are no specific "
"extensions to differentiate between different types of dataset, serial vs. "
"distributed data or static vs. temporal data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:34
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:36
msgid "How to stay informed?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:38
msgid ""
"We keep a [status](vtkhdf_status.md) page up to date, that tracks current "
"status of the VTKHDF specification and implementation in the `vtkHDFReader` "
"and `vtkHDFWriter`. Bug tracking and proposals are tracked in a [Gitlab "
"issue](https://gitlab.kitware.com/vtk/vtk/-/issues/19243). Additionally, all "
"VTKHDF issues are [tagged appropriately](https://gitlab.kitware.com/vtk/"
"vtk/-/issues/?"
"sort=created_date&state=opened&label_name%5B%5D=area%3AVTKHDF&first_page_size=20) "
"as `area:VTKHDF`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:40
msgid "Where should we create a proposal for the file format?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../vtk_file_formats/vtkhdf_file_format/vtkhdf_introduction.md:42
msgid ""
"The VTKHDF File Format is not considered complete, and lacks support for "
"some VTK data types. This specification is led by the community; please post "
"ideas and design for new data types on the [VTK discourse](https://discourse."
"vtk.org/). This Discourse will be made into a Gitlab issue once VTKHDF "
"contributors have agreed on a design."
msgstr ""

